{"tid":997796,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【等足15年】安妮夏菲維透露《走佬俏公主》拍第三集","createTime":"2019-01-27T12:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T13:07:10.000Z","uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2075c9aef9ee3837874f2332181dd544785fdc2e","tid":997796,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548485702_ebbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548485702_ebbf.jpg&h=75f2b70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安妮夏菲維透露《走佬俏公主》拍第三集<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548485708_9b74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548485708_9b74.jpg&h=12cf6e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安妮夏菲維亮相節目《Watch What Happens Live with Andy Cohen》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548485709_718d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548485709_718d.jpg&h=45939d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n透露與茱莉安德絲都期望開拍第三集<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548485720_7bf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548485720_7bf3.jpg&h=94380ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安妮夏菲維靠《走佬俏公主》走紅<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548485720_e60d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548485720_e60d.jpg&h=5abe8e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《走佬俏公主》第二集於2014年推出<br />\n美國女星安妮夏菲維（Anne Hathaway）靠電影《走佬俏公主》（The Princess Diaries）成名，電影首集於2001年公開後，於2004年推出第二集，這15年來一直有傳會開拍新一集，但消息都未獲得證實。<br />\n近日安妮夏菲維亮相節目《Watch What Happens Live with Andy Cohen》時，終於透露第三集正在籌備階段：「第三集的劇集正在撰寫，我想拍，Julie（茱莉安德絲）想拍，監製Debra Martin Chase都想拍，我們真的希望能成功開拍。」安妮又說電影團隊與影迷一樣愛這部電影，所以要待一切準備好才會開始拍攝。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190126/59188395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F59188395&d=6cLUeJot05wT1KwRYHvTdgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=55ab412d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F59188395&h=df238dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190126/59188395</a>"},{"pid":"93ae8999040b4d98e12ac0bb5549e9072efd24a5","tid":997796,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"就快變走佬俏中女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970ec880a694278b19100102e2b5e09a8a764cdc","tid":997796,"uid":96708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"希望唔洗等到Julie andrews過身先拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然又做cg人面都得....廸記最鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac283eba6716c45899c0e3d69f7bdd0f140af77","tid":997796,"uid":162073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"安妮永遠都咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba1de59f75dfffdfb9d2d2d7426b90222ceec1d","tid":997796,"uid":187378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:07:10.000Z","msg":"希望Chris pine做返男主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im